node.text: but I think you could all use a good laugh! I challenge you NOT to laugh out loud at this!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Misery on July 29, 2021. May be an image of 4 people, people standing, outdoors and text that says 'Grants to Become a Teacher!'.

node.text: I can never predict what people will like, what they will ignore, and what will piss people off. But here's something we can all laugh at! The fact that this ad had to copy and paste the same few people over and over to create a line of people trying to become teachers! 😄?🤷

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Teacher Misery on July 29, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'PSYPOST.ORG Lower cognitive ability linked to non-compliance with social distancing guidelines during the coronavirus Eric Hosemann and 47 others 21 Comments 8 Shares Comment Share I don't know what "lower cognitive ability" means, but certainly won't wear a mask ever'.

node.text: I believe the term I'm looking for is "Whoop! There it is!"

It's gonna be a FUN year!"'.
